    dc:creator "Jewell, Tony" ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of Hemiandrus (Orthoptera: Anostostomatidae) from Fiordland National Park, New Zealand" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177899>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177898> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177899>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6: The eight species of Hemiandrus presently known from Fiordland National Park, New Zealand, comparing typical color patterns: A) H. fiordensis (Salmon); B) H. focalis (Hutton); C) H. nitaweta n. sp.; D) H. superba n. sp.; E) H. sp. “ madisylvestris ” (Johns, 2001); F) H. sp. “ Hunter Mountains ” (pers. obs.); G) H. maculifrons (Walker) and H) H. sp. “ Esperance Valley ” (pers. obs.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177899/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177898>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5: Holotype of Hemiandrus nitaweta n. sp. in preserved state, showing A) ventral profile, B) lateral profile and C) head, frontal profile." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

